Params: {3: 'Shark-speare crumbles, letting off distorted noises, then collapses in front of you.'}
{3: "With Liv's support, you slowly lie on the ground."}
{3: 'The sky of the theme park fills your vision. The faint traces of the moon and the stars in daylight bespeckle the clear blue of the summer skies.'}
{3: '...What did they call this again? A holiday? President Hassen needs to get that overtime pay ready. Double.'}
{3: '...And, a detailed report about Luna and Shome would have to be written too. Best get the Engineering Force in to just blow the place up and rebuild it as well.'}
{3: "...As for what's in Shome's spine... Well, let's forget about that. As long as it's in the report, Asimov will sort it out."}
{3: '...With things finally at an end, a wave of fatigue washes over. Eyelids... drooping...'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: "You guys take care of Commandant for a while. I'll call for reinforcements.", 4: '1'}
{3: 'Meanwhile, in a high place that overlooks the plaza...'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Luna', 3: 'Inelegant, but our goal has been achieved.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Luna', 3: 'Our goodbyes will have to wait until another day.', 4: '1'}
{3: 'Luna leaps high into the air, then twists and dissipates, melting into the sky.'}
